modName: Sword of the Seeker by FavoredSoul DSR Patch
summary: Yet a Small patch for a sword made by Favoredsoul ,made to work with dual sheath redux by Neovalen. With Sheath too! Compatible with HDT Equipment.
descriptionHtml:
Original Mod Page: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/83894/?]Sword of the Seeker by FavoredSoul
[/url]DSR: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34155/?]Dual Sheath Redux By Neovalen[/url]

Install with any mod managers(Nexus or MO).Install this first, Delete Old DSR Patch, Re-run the procer, Profit!.
Enjoy!

Need a patch for a certain Weapon mod?
Don't hesitate to ask or comment at this mod page. :)
